{"type": "article", "id": 17107, "title": "钢圈吊灯", "description": "", "date": "2015-11-05T10:11:06Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 29, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606160209JOgDbZ1qVMhnk7Iu.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这是来自意大利设计师 Luis Arrivillaga 的吊灯，它的灯罩是由两个钢圈做的半球组成，可以完全重叠，就像将灯罩打来。这盏灯的亮点在灯光通过钢圈射出后投射下来的阴影，在墙上或地上形成可以变化的纹路，很有艺术感。<a href=\"http://luisarrivillaga.com/\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261442554pzsAPv8UMiDgXW6.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"850\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.41666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144256JyRNpHCFVj10s24Q.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"772\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.71481481\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144256EYiDHaCtnSMWoAkv.jpg\" width=\"467\" height=\"661\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.41541756\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144257dzJX4Y0ti9uSbIw3.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"850\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.41666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}